title: Womens Moxie Pull-On Barrel Jeans Mid-Low Rise Boyfriend Drawstring Baggy Jeans Elastic Waist Stretchy Denim Pants
description: Relaxed & Stylish Fit: Features a low-rise, slouchy silhouette with tapered legs, offering both comfort and a trendy streetwear vibe.
Breathable Elastic Fabric: Crafted from a pure cotton denim fabric that feels like sweatpants, providing exceptional breathability and stretch for all-day comfort.
Adjustable Elastic Waistband: Designed with a high-elastic adjustable waistband and button accents, ensuring a perfect fit for a wide range of sizes.
Unique Details: Distressed elements, paint splatter accents, oversized patch pockets, and a contrast drawstring waist add both functionality and character.
Versatile Style Staple: Easily pairs with sneakers or boots, making it a perfect choice for casual outings or elevated everyday looks.
